                <span class="skill-item"><i class="devicon-postgresql-plain"></i> PostgreSQL</span>
                <span class="skill-item"><i class="devicon-git-plain"></i> Git / GitHub</span>
                <span class="skill-item"><i class="devicon-jira-plain"></i> Jira</span>
                <span class="skill-item"><i class="devicon-figma-plain"></i> Figma / XD</span>
                <span class="skill-item">✦ Claude Code</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
